7,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T04:40:08.000Z","msg":"juno : 02 年嗰陣有好多新人<br />\n徐繼宗：係囉 有蕭正楠<br />\njerald : 仲有Twins <br />\n<br />\n好提唔提提呢兩個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T04:59:44.000Z","msg":"Twins應該早過Juno一年"},{"pid":"92f4861310022aa185315481f82bcede26cfcaa3","tid":2097739,"uid":35221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T05:01:07.000Z","msg":"稱被誤導下購公司股份 商人追麥浚龍父2.2億元<br />\n 社會 17:45 2018/12/11<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2225000/2228079/dcmn20091218014_1024_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2225000%2F2228079%2Fdcmn20091218014_1024_1024.jpg&h=5e41644b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 歌手麥浚龍父親、上市公司中建置地（0261）主席麥紹棠。（經濟日報資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n歌手麥浚龍父親、上市公司中建置地（0261）主席麥紹棠，遭1名商人入稟高等法院索償2.2億元。商人指麥紹棠於前年聲稱將獲解放軍支持的內地公司收購，保證若購入其公司股份可賺6,000萬元，商人遂以每股0.035元購入60億股份。其後收購失敗，股價大跌至0.008元，商人指受誤導下才與麥達成協議，遂入稟向麥索償2.22億元。<br />\n<br />\n原告吳健南，答辯人麥紹棠。入稟狀指，原告於前年1月經友人認識麥紹棠，麥當時稱其公司將由有解放軍支持的新興鑄管股份有限公司收購，擬注資12億元，一但宣布收購，股價必升。<br />\n<br />\n原告指麥亦提及有意出售所持股份，遂提出以每股0.035元出售60億股予原告，並保證於半年內賺6,000萬元，若有任何損失，由被告作出賠償。原告其後於麥安排下與新興鑄管代表晚膳，其後原告決定接納麥的建議，並於同年3月完成交易。<br />\n<br />\n惟至同年6月，中建置地宣布收購計劃失敗，同年10月，股價跌至0.008元。及至今年8月，原告指其友人與麥會面，麥承認因缺乏資金證明而收購失敗。原告指有關收購說法屬誤導，以前年10月每股0.008元計算，要求麥賠償1.62億元，以及麥保證可賺的6,000萬元，共索償2.22億元等損失。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2228079/稱被誤導下購公司股份%E3%80%80商人追麥浚龍父2.2億元\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2228079%2F%E7%A8%B1%E8%A2%AB%E8%AA%A4%E5%B0%8E%E4%B8%8B%E8%B3%BC%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E8%82%A1%E4%BB%BD%25E3%2580%2580%E5%95%86%E4%BA%BA%E8%BF%BD%E9%BA%A5%E6%B5%9A%E9%BE%8D%E7%88%B62.2%E5%84%84%E5%85%83&d=uYDAXyhVPN7xTSuHIXBXEuExUl64GHAvDQsppiVFus8%3D&h=4a0fbc98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2228079/稱被誤導下購公司股份%E3%80%80商人追麥浚龍父2.2億元</a>"},{"pid":"8b83cbb9dc06a53fa173c8be2e1de95bf9efccf7","tid":2097739,"uid":56999,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T05:03:59.000Z","msg":"爹地 佢地蝦我"},{"pid":"96581f5c2f598a67fba8b897cd7edc7b2b0a4ec1","tid":2097739,"uid":14333,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"f275115b8c44233c3400a054a3fe7c5855aef3c8","tid":2097739,"uid":160051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bc16659f3f7f2c0cd17652fdfae5d74626a05ab","tid":2097739,"uid":14333,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T04:40:08.000Z","msg":"juno : 02 年嗰陣有好多新人<br />\n徐繼宗：係囉 有蕭正楠<br />\njerald : 仲有Twins <br />\n<br />\n好提唔提提呢兩個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T04:59:44.000Z","msg":"Twins應該早過Juno一年"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T05:04:19.000Z","msg":"yes Jerald 都即刻更正左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08be2fea0769e6e6ac10a9de1b241a1ef695d221","tid":2097739,"uid":211461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T05:05:01.000Z","msg":"愛上殺手乜唔係cover韓仔嘅咩"},{"pid":"1e3ec97d7b0cd79ccb3fa3464410e3b13de6a9f7","tid":2097739,"uid":54923,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T05:09:39.000Z","msg":"有錢咪可以咁玩囉 冇錢 比咩你都要做嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"832e9290caec3227a8a010e0e4b24fa96f571860","tid":2097739,"uid":82917,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T05:10:44.000Z","msg":"痴撚線董折同蒲咩心呢個concept聽撚左幾年仲玩緊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"163b8b0d5a3a143ab61850a777af414e227af465","tid":2097739,"uid":81562,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"832e9290caec3227a8a010e0e4b24fa96f571860","tid":2097739,"uid":82917,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"